📊 Key Insights

Benefits of Normalization
- Brings all features to a common scale.
- Prevents features with larger values from dominating the model.
- Improves convergence speed in optimization-based algorithms.
- Enhances performance of distance-based algorithms.

Impact on Machine Learning Models:

1. Logistic Regression
- Performance generally improves after normalization.
- Faster and more stable model training.

2. Distance-Based Models (KNN, SVM)
- Significantly benefit from normalized data.
- More accurate distance calculations.

3. Tree-Based Models
- Minimal impact because decision trees do not depend on feature scales.

